[30;1m1776 | [0m[35mdef ignore_comments(string):[0m
[30;1m1777 | [0m[35m    """Ignore comments in given string by replacing them with spaces. This[0m
[30;1m1778 | [0m[35m    reduces the parsing time by roughly a factor of two.[0m
